
---

## 🚫 **.gitignore - Copy and Paste**

```gitignore
# Byte-compiled files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so

# Virtual environments
.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/
pythonenv*

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
*.code-workspace

# Jupyter Notebook
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# Model files (large)
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.keras
*.pb
*.ckpt
*.weights
*.bin
*.safetensors

# Tokenizer files (optional - keep if small)
# tokenizer/

# Model directories
model/
saved_models/
results/
output/
logs/

# Data files (large)
data/
*.arrow
*.jsonl

# Training outputs
checkpoints/
*.log
*.out

# OS specific files
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Python testing
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# System files
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib